@host = http://localhost:8080
@username = zhangsan
@password = 123456
@token = 请先登录后替换这里
@templateId = 1
@recordId = 1

### 1. 登录获取 JWT
POST {{host}}/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 2. 测试流式优化接口
POST {{host}}/api/prompt-optimizations/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: text/event-stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "templateId": {{templateId}},
  "originalPrompt": "请为一款面向大学生的 AI 笔记软件生成产品介绍文案",
  "target": "提升表达清晰度，并明确输出结构",
  "outputFormat": "分点输出，包含标题、核心卖点、结尾行动号召"
}

### 预期会持续收到 SSE 事件，阶段通常包括：
### REVIEW -> ANALYSIS -> OPTIMIZING -> TOKEN(多次) -> DONE
### DONE 事件 content 示例：
### {"recordId":1,"score":85,"riskLevel":"LOW"}

### 3. 将优化结果保存为正式 Prompt
POST {{host}}/api/prompt-optimizations/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recordId": {{recordId}},
  "title": "AI 笔记软件产品介绍文案优化版",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "tags": "AI,文案,产品介绍",
  "visibility": "public"
}
